          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Level Select -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At the title screen hold Up + Left + Select and press Circle</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; 2 Player Battle Mode -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Enter the level select code. One of the avaliable options should be 2 player battle mode</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite Continues -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">When you've used your last continue and the ''continue'' countdown comes up with the words ''game over'' flashing in your corner of the screen, just hold the triangle and select buttons and press start. You'll get five additional continues. Repeat as needed</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite lives -
